didn't become your mom,

30
00:02:15,750 --> 00:02:16,850
are you really disappointed?

31
00:02:17,520 --> 00:02:18,380
Not really.

32
00:02:19,520 --> 00:02:19,890
Grandma,

33
00:02:20,680 --> 00:02:21,410
Dad likes

34
00:02:21,430 --> 00:02:22,500
what he likes.

35
00:02:23,000 --> 00:02:24,500
I like what I like.

36
00:02:25,280 --> 00:02:26,980
My dad's feelings come first.

37
00:02:27,800 --> 00:02:29,500
Mine come after.

38
00:02:30,190 --> 00:02:31,260
I'm easygoing.

39
00:02:38,400 --> 00:02:39,780
There's a package for you.

40
00:02:40,520 --> 00:02:41,100
For me?

41
00:02:44,310 --> 00:02:45,170
You haven't finished eating yet.

42
00:02:46,030 --> 00:02:46,780
Grandma, I'm full.

43
00:02:48,800 --> 00:02:49,410
A figure.

44
00:02:50,280 --> 00:02:51,500
Who sent this to me?

45
00:02:51,800 --> 00:02:52,850
I didn't buy anything.

46
00:02:54,150 --> 00:02:54,780
Strange.

47
00:03:00,280 --> 00:03:00,780
I got it.

48
00:03:01,520 --> 00:03:03,780
I'll do my homework in my room.

49
00:03:07,280 --> 00:03:08,660
I also think the gaming industry

50
00:03:09,030 --> 00:03:10,290
is promising.

51
00:03:11,190 --> 00:03:12,890
Hope we'll collaborate in the future.

52
00:03:13,310 --> 00:03:14,780
Real estate should be viable.

53
00:03:15,630 --> 00:03:16,260
Yes.

54
00:03:16,870 --> 00:03:18,690
Let me properly introduce you now.

55
00:03:18,870 --> 00:03:19,410
Zu

56
00:03:19,800 --> 00:03:22,130
is the President
of Shengnuo Real Estate,

57
00:03:22,310 --> 00:03:23,260
and I'm

58
00:03:23,280 --> 00:03:25,890
the Project Manager
of the East District

59
00:03:25,910 --> 00:03:26,780
Sports Industry Park project.

60
00:03:27,000 --> 00:03:28,410
Without any experience in real estate,

61
00:03:28,680 --> 00:03:30,780
can you handle this big project

62
00:03:31,120 --> 00:03:31,660
right off the bat?

63
00:03:32,310 --> 00:03:34,130
Although she has no experience,

64
00:03:34,590 --> 00:03:35,500
she has provided us

65
00:03:35,520 --> 00:03:36,660
with very valuable advice.

66
00:03:37,030 --> 00:03:38,730
And if she hadn't had the capability,

67
00:03:39,150 --> 00:03:40,780
I wouldn't have made her
my project manager,

68
00:03:40,800 --> 00:03:41,290
would I?

69
00:03:41,520 --> 00:03:43,890
So your company got that land?

70
00:03:44,280 --> 00:03:45,290
It's my friend's company.

71
00:03:45,680 --> 00:03:47,340
Your friend's company got the land

72
00:03:48,000 --> 00:03:48,890
and let you develop it?

73
00:03:49,150 --> 00:03:50,130
We're developing it jointly.

74
00:03:50,150 --> 00:03:51,610
Developing the old district

75
