involves a lot of things.

76
00:03:52,910 --> 00:03:55,260
It'll take a long time to get approvals,

77
00:03:55,280 --> 00:03:57,500
yet you've started planning already?

78
00:03:57,800 --> 00:03:58,980
Seems you know quite a bit about it.

79
00:03:59,630 --> 00:04:00,660
My friend's company has taken care

80
00:04:00,680 --> 00:04:02,260
of these tedious procedures,

81
00:04:02,870 --> 00:04:04,130
Shuhan can just get right to work.

82
00:04:06,800 --> 00:04:07,980
Seems your business is doing very well.

83
00:04:09,910 --> 00:04:11,380
Cut it out.

84
00:04:12,150 --> 00:04:12,980
What's with all the questions?

85
00:04:13,280 --> 00:04:13,820
Besides,

86
00:04:14,560 --> 00:04:15,290
the project is not that big.

87
00:04:15,400 --> 00:04:16,410
What makes you think I can't handle it?

88
00:04:16,920 --> 00:04:18,900
After all, I was quite a big shot

89
00:04:18,920 --> 00:04:20,610
in East District back in the day.

90
00:04:21,120 --> 00:04:21,660
I can get it done

91
00:04:21,680 --> 00:04:23,250
with just a few phone calls.

92
00:04:23,920 --> 00:04:25,370
You're worrying over nothing.

93
00:04:25,920 --> 00:04:26,900
Real estate isn't as easy

94
00:04:26,920 --> 00:04:28,490
to make money in as it used to be.

95
00:04:28,680 --> 00:04:30,100
But if it can improve

96
00:04:30,120 --> 00:04:31,460
people's quality of life,

97
00:04:31,920 --> 00:04:33,140
there will be business opportunities.

98
00:04:35,920 --> 00:04:37,020
You really have great taste,

99
00:04:37,270 --> 00:04:39,140
especially in choosing an amazing girl

100
00:04:39,160 --> 00:04:40,100
to be your girlfriend.

101
00:04:41,000 --> 00:04:42,730
I wish my bestie

102
00:04:43,000 --> 00:04:43,900
everlasting happiness.

103
00:04:44,190 --> 00:04:45,900
But I must make one thing clear.

104
00:04:46,800 --> 00:04:48,100
Don't bully her.

105
00:04:48,190 --> 00:04:49,370
If you mistreat her,

106
00:04:49,390 --> 00:04:51,290
we won't let you get away with it.

107
00:04:52,270 --> 00:04:52,900
Of course.

108
00:04:55,040 --> 00:04:55,410
Cheers!

109
00:04:59,190 --> 00:05:00,140
Is he a decent guy?

110
00:05:01,040 --> 00:05:02,140
Can't say it here?

111
00:05:02,160 --> 00:05:03,100
Let's talk about it later.

112
00:05:15,510 --> 00:05:16,290
Ms. Tan,

113
00:05:16,510 --> 00:05:18,370
is the street dance figure from you?

114
00:05:20,800 --> 00:05:21,370
Do you like it?

115
00:05:22,680 --> 00:05:23,250
Yes.

116
00:05:23,630 --> 00:05:24,660
Thank you.

117
00:05:35,040 --> 00:05:35,780
Stop playing.

118
00:05:36,430 --> 00:05:37,140
Go do your homework.

119
00:05:37,390 --> 00:05:38,250
If I catch you playing,

120
00:05:38,270 --> 00:05:39,780
I'll confiscate all of them.

121
00:05:41,190 --> 00:05:41,850
Be self-disciplined.

122
00:06:07,480 --> 00:06:08,050
Le,

123
00:06:09,360 --> 00:06:10,100
hurry up.

124
00:06:15,480 --> 00:06:15,980
Sweetheart,

125
00:06:17,120 --> 00:06:17,700
wake up.

126
00:06:19,120 --> 00:06:19,610
Did you hear me?

127
00:06:20,120 --> 00:06:20,370
Come on.

128
00:06:20,720 --> 00:06:20,980
Get up.

129
00:06:22,160 --> 00:06:22,580
Quickly.

130
00:06:23,750 --> 00:06:24,050
Come on.

131
00:06:25,750 --> 00:06:26,250
Go.

132
00:06:47,120 --> 00:06:48,100
Enough with this.

133
00:06:49,240 --> 00:06:50,370
Now is not the time.

134
00:06:52,000 --> 00:06:52,980
It's okay.

135
00:06:53,120 --> 00:06:53,850
It's a holiday today.

136
00:06:54,240 --> 00:06:54,850
Besides,

137
00:06:55,480 --> 00:06:57,580
he'll have less time with this
in middle school.

138
00:06:58,750 --> 00:07:00,100
Who is spoiling him now?

139
00:07:03,120 --> 00:07:03,980
You're good in every way,

140
00:07:05,480 --> 00:07:06,340
except for your studies.

141
00:07:08,070 --> 00:07:09,460
Your father was an excellent student.

142
00:07:10,000 --> 00:07:11,140
I never had to worry about him.

143
00:07:12,270 --> 00:07:13,580
I wonder who you take after.

144
00:07:14,950 --> 00:07:16,580
Grades aren't everything.

145
00:07:17,720 --> 00:07:20,460
I think he's doing well in all aspects.

146
00:07:21,240 --> 00:07:22,220
My dad is the best.

147
00:07:25,000 --> 00:07:26,100
Have you done your homework?

148
00:07:26,830 --> 00:07:27,250
Grandma,

149
00:07:28,120 --> 00:07:30,020
